{"type": "article", "id": 24534, "title": "简洁的家用茶具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144035alExAZD0WdeU6PbC.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组陶瓷茶具来自西班牙设计工作室 Lagranja，包括水壶、罐子和可加热的无线感应底座。水壶把手和底座的边缘都是木质的，搭配白色的磁壶，突出了茶具的简洁。而圆形底座也让加热变得方便且美观。设计师想要让这些存在于厨房的工具也能运用于客厅等场所，以此适应越来越小的居住空间。<a href=\"http://lagranjadesign.com/cooking-tableware/?lang=en\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144031vloGHwjcN4dWe0CQ.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.79681275\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144032ZqOETXdjeALFSkN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440338dP9FSOCRANEaWQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144033j9NHwi74P8ZlhQzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144034xeSzLMWjCN1mFG3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}